comment: George (IND) makes incidental contact with Smith (CLE) during rebounding.
Young (IND) and James (CLE) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Young (IND) makes marginal contact with James (CLE) that does not affect his SQBR.
Smith (CLE) makes incidental contact with George (IND) that does not affect his SQBR.
Frye (CLE) makes contact to George's (IND) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of IND possession is overturned and CLE is awarded possession.
Korver (CLE) sets the screen on Young (IND) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
James (CLE) makes incidental contact with George (IND) after the pass.
Teague (IND) makes incidental contact with Smith (CLE) that does not affect his SQBR.
James (CLE) makes marginal contact with Teague (IND) off ball.
IND is correctly assessed a delay of game violation.
Smith (CLE) makes incidental contact with George (IND) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Young (IND) commits a take foul on James (CLE).
Miles (IND) does not make contact with the ball while part of it still remains in the cylinder above the basket ring.
George (IND) makes marginal contact with Korver (CLE) that does not affect his FOM off ball.
Young (IND) commits a take foul on James (CLE).
Teague (IND) enters the area inside the three-point line prior to the free throw being released.
Shumpert (CLE) makes marginal contact with Miles (IND) that does not affect his FOM off ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] George (IND) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Young (IND) makes contact with the ball and any contact with Thompson (CLE) is considered incidental.
Turner (IND) commits a take foul on Smith (CLE).
Thompson (CLE) allows Miles (IND) to land following the jump shot attempt.
Teague (IND) commits a take foul on Williams (CLE).
